videos.description: Virginia's London Perrantes cuts into the lane, then drops a floater over the outstretched hands of a Miami defender.
videos.headline: Perrantes drains floater over defender for Virginia

videos.description: Miami's Anthony Lawrence Jr. dishes to Ebuku Izundu who turns and dunks it in.
videos.headline: Good pass sets up Izundu two-handed slam for Miami

videos.description: Miami's Bruce Brown steals a pass and sprints up floor, but misses an easy dunk.
videos.headline: Brown misses easy dunk for Miami

videos.description: Virginia head coach Tony Bennett talks about his team's offensive struggles in the first half and what his team must do better in the second half.
videos.headline: Virginia head coach Tony Bennett on his team's offensive struggles

videos.description: Virginia's Mamadi Diakite almost travels, but drops the ball then turns and hits a jumper and draws a foul.
videos.headline: Diakite scores on crazy and-1

videos.description: Virginia's Darius Thompson tosses a great bounce pass to Mamadi Diakite who finishes with a dunk.
videos.headline: Thompson sets up Diakite slam

videos.description: Miami's Dejan Vasiljevic hits a catch and shoot 3-pointer in the left corner to tie the game with under a minute remaining.
videos.headline: Vasiljevic hits crucial three for Miami

videos.description: Miami's Davon Reed tosses up a shot as the clock expires to win the game, but after further review the shot would not count.
videos.headline: Reed's incredible buzzer-beater waved off in win

videos.description: Miami's Bruce Brown connects on  a crucial 3-pointer late in overtime to give Miami the win.
videos.headline: Brown drills huge 3-pointer to put Miami up for good

videos.description: Miami head coach Jim Larrañaga on his team's huge conference win at Virginia.
videos.headline: Larrañaga: "Our young guys really stepped up"
